How do you create interactive widgets in Streamlit? Provide examples

Streamlit offers a range of interactive widgets that allow users to interact with your app, modifying parameters, selecting options, or entering values dynamically. 
Here are examples of some commonly used interactive widgets:

Streamlit.checkbox() - this gives us a checkbox
streamlit.selectbox() - this gives us a dropdown of values that the user can select.
streamlit.multiselect() - this gives a dropdown of values from which the user can select multiple values.
streamlit.button() - this helps us to create buttons.
There are many more widgets that can be used in streamlit with just few lines.
